      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! Whether you're cruising on the weekend or just want a reliable, stunning ride, this car is a total dream to drive. I've taken meticulous care of it, and I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
