    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This A80-generation icon is a masterclass in 90s over-engineering, presented in concours-level condition. At its heart lies the 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, paired with the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical synchronization is flawless, with the sequential turbos delivering linear boost pressure across the rev range. The chassis retains its original rigidity, supported by a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential for precise power delivery. From the four-piston magnesium-alloy calipers to the untouched wiring harness, this vehicle represents a rare, unmodified specimen of automotive excellence.",
